These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, country, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | country | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, rabbit
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | goldfish | rabbit | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, trike, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | trike | motorbike | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, card-games, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | card-games | gardening |

 #################################

 
