.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, puzzles, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is reading##2
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | puzzles | card-games | reading |

